    <item>
      <title>Nudge 1.2.1</title>
      <description><![CDATA[
        <h2>Nudge 1.2.1</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Apple traffic lights are now built into the minimized HUD — red hides the app, yellow tucks it away</li>
          <li>Expand chevron moved to the bottom-right of the HUD to clear room for the traffic lights</li>
          <li>Expanded-view wordmark shifted right so the traffic lights sit comfortably on the rounded surface</li>
          <li>Sparkle update check tightened to every 5 minutes</li>
        </ul>
      ]]></description>
